    <p style="max-width: 900px; margin: auto; font-size: 1.1rem;">
        Our school proudly promotes multicultural understanding and actively works to combat racism. We organize integration days, cultural exchange events, and workshops on equality, respect, and tolerance.
    </p>
</section>

